<title>USA: BankAmerica expands stock option plan.</title>
<headline>BankAmerica expands stock option plan.</headline>
<dateline>SAN FRANCISCO 1997-05-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>BankAmerica Corp said it expanded its global employee stock option program to include 3,500 more employees in 24 countries outside the U.S.</p>
<p>They join about 85,000 BankAmerica employees who received their first grant of options when the program was launched by Chairman and Chief Executive Dave Coulter November 19.</p>
<p>The grant price of the November 19, 1996 grant was $95.18. The grant price is equal to the average of the high and low prices of BankAmerica shares on the day of the grant.</p>
